### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
### BENEFICIOS ENDPOINTS
###

### 1. Get all benefits
GET {{baseUrl}}/beneficios
Authorization: {{token}}

### 2. Get benefit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3. Create new benefit
POST {{baseUrl}}/beneficios
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Descuento en cafetería",
  "descripcion": "Obtén un descuento del 10% en todas las compras de la cafetería del campus",
  "tipo": "DESCUENTO",
  "valor": 10,
  "comercioId": 1,
  "activo": true
}

### 4. Update benefit
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Descuento actualizado",
  "valor": 15
}

### 5. Delete benefit
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 6. Get benefits by commerce
GET {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/commerce/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 7. Get user's redeemed benefits
GET {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/redeemed
Authorization: {{token}}

### 8. Redeem benefit
POST {{baseUrl}}/beneficios/1/redeem
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
